result.title: Invitation to PRAYAAS, Technex'15
result.content:
Hello world,

Technex '15 (IIT BHU) presents you,

PRAYAAS

There will be WAR and CODE will flow.

This is a 5hr online ACM_ICPC style Algorithmic programming contest, under the flagship of Byte the Bits, Technex '15 (IIT BHU).

You get 11 questions, 300 minutes and a prize money of INR 70,000 at stake.

Event sponsor : Microsoft
Event partner: codechef.com
Event Date: 28 th Feb (2PM â€” 7PM IST)

Contest Link: http://www.codechef.com/PRYS2015/

Please find the event time in your timezone here: http://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?msg=Prayaas+2015&iso=20150228T14&p1=54&ah=5

We hope to see you there in the contest.

Please join our facebook event page to stay updated with the contest information.
